Text.Value: Saw the crash... came quick... try 'n help folk...
Why didn't you notice the brains?
Elf... ran north... up the beach...
*The corpse does not stir. It will answer no more questions.*

EditorData.AnimationTags: Murat - SwD - Tong out of the jerked mouth.

Text.Value: Went west... others followed... couldn't help 'emselves...
*The spell's power wanes. You can ask no more questions.*

Synopsis: You speak with the dead soul of a fisherman, who hurried to the crash site when he saw your ship fall from the sky. At the site he saw a mindflayer, disguised as a beautiful woman, and was killed by Intellect Devourers (brains).
